rating_comment:
Excellent place to stay. Once a small cleaning issue was pointed out it was done to the best standard.
Very communicative host. Safe and peaceful place to stay.
If you are in Dhaka this is almost a 5 star place to stay.
Beats staying in cramped hotel room.any dat.
